<h5>Redesign of the thoughtbot Blog</h5>
<h6>September 2014</h6>

<hr>

<p>Thoughtbot went through a small rebrand in 2014. We updated our brand
colors, logo, and typeface. We've also been making efforts to showcase our
design capabilities.</p>

<p>I wrote a blog post that is a more <%= link_to 'in-depth description',
  'http://robots.thoughtbot.com/human-centered-type' %> of how treating the
  text as an interface in our blog influenced the design.</p>

